00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:21,680
change in the spread's price, but as we

723
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:23,480
know, we have to multiply that by 100,

724
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:26,480
and we get an actual profit of $2

725
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,740
,775.

726
00:30:29,340 --> 00:30:34,140
The breakeven price at expiration is $777.75,

727
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:37,680
and if the spread is right at $777

728
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:41,560
.75 at expiration, the 800 put that I

