00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:04,980
put spread was $39.84 at expiration, or

798
00:34:04,980 --> 00:34:08,860
a value of $3,984.

799
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:11,880
And so if I bought this put spread

800
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:16,780
